rse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20he%20inherited%2018%20acres%20of%20land%20from%20his%20father.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20read%20Rachel%20Carson%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98Silent%20Spring%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20highlighted%20the%20environmental%20harm%20caused%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20use%20of%20pesticides.%20Motivated%20by%20Carson%E2%80%99s%20message%2C%20Neelam%20resolved%20to%20transition%20his%20land%20into%20an%20organic%20farm.%20By%202003%2C%20he%20had%20successfully%20converted%20his%20entire%20acreage%20to%20organic%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20switching%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%20I%20found%20out%20there%20were%20no%20organic%20seed%20varieties%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20some%20were%20accessible%20for%20rice%2C%20none%20were%20available%20for%20vegetables.%20The%20absence%20of%20reserves%20or%20authenticity%20in%20seed%20sources%20was%20concerning.%20Instead%2C%20the%20market%20was%20saturated%20with%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20seeds.%20This%20was%20a%20big%20worrying%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20also%20observed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20Northeast%20were%20switching%20to%20hybrid%20seeds%20and%20overlooked%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315599%2Fhyderabad-chandana-naveen-gade-seedbasket-agro-services-sell-native-seeds-to-urban-gardeners%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheirloom%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20only%20hybrid%20seeds%20were%20to%20be%20supplied%20to%20the%20market%20to%20the%20farmers.%20This%20was%20never%20a%20solution%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98evergreen%E2%80%99%20revolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20o