rong%20opposing%20political%20views%20today%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20rallies%20within%2030%20km%20of%20each%20other.%20While%20Ms%20Banerjee%20labelled%20the%20BJP%20worse%20than%20a%20snake%20--%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20trust%20a%20snake%20and%20even%20pet%20it%2C%20but%20not%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B%20---%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20addressed%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20the%20burning%20political%20issue%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act.%20But%20his%20defence%20was%20crouched%20in%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20--%20the%20CAA%20is%20being%20tarred%20to%20remove%20attention%20from%20corruption%2C%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Ms%20Banerjee%20or%20her%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(INDIA%20bloc)%20never%20cared%20for%20the%20marginalised%20communities.%20Now%20that%20we%20have%20brought%20CAA%2C%20they%20are%20spreading%20rumours%20and%20lies.%20It%20is%20Modi%20ki%20guarantee%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20those%20who%20have%20faith%20in%20Maa%20Bharati%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20this%20evening%2C%20addressing%20a%20rally%20at%20the%20Rash%20Mela%20grounds%20in%20Cooch%20Behar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20saying%20remove%20corruption%3B%20the%20opposition%20is%20saying%20'save%20the%20corrupt.'%20I%20will%20ensure%20the%20corrupt%20are%20punished%2C%20and%20the%20poor%20get%20justice.%20In%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20more%20stringent%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20corrupt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20reference%20to%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20hot%20button%20issue%20in%20this%20election.%C2%A0%20While%20Trinamool%20was%20trying%20to%20save%20the%20culprits%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20BJP's%20focus%20is%20empowering%20the%20women.%20The%20culprits%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20will%20spend%20their%20lives%20in%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20issue%20was%20addressed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Cooch%20Behar%20around%20noon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20one%20registers%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20one%20will%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20from%20Bangladesh%20and%20they%20will%20lose%20all%20basic%20rights%2C%20she%20told%20her%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20you%20submit%20your%20name%20for%20registration%2C%20you%20will%20be%20declared%20a%20Bangladeshi.%20This%20means%20you%20will%20not%20get%20the%20benefits%20under%20Lakhishree%2C%20Kanyashee%2C%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20vote%2C%20you%20will%20not%20have%20citizenship%20rights%2C%20government%20rights.%20Think%20yourself%20whether%20it%20is%20good%20or%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CAA%20is%20a%20trap%20to%20turn%20legal%20citizens%20into%20foreigners.%20Once%20you%20(BJP)%20implement%20CAA%2C%20NRC%20will%20follow...%20Remember%20CAA%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20fish%2C%20the%20tail%20is%20the%20NRC%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20snake%20analogy%20to%20claim%20the%20BJp%20is%20not%20to%20be%20trusted..%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20allow%20neither%20CAA%20nor%20NRC%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20If%20you%20apply%2C%20you%20will%20be%20designated%20as%20foreigners%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%2025%20of%20the%20state's%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20coming%20election%2C%20a%20chunk%20of%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20from%20north%20Bengal%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20consolidated%20its%20base%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20re-nominated%20the%20sitting%20MP%2C%20junior%20home%20minister%20Nisith%20Pramanik%2C%20from%20Cooch%20Behar.%C2%A0%20The%20Trinamool%20has%20fielded%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20of%20Sitai%2C%20Rajbanshi%20community%20member%20Jagadish%20Barma%20Basunia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20claimed%20today%20that%20the%20minister%20is%20a%20Trinamool%20reject.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20national%20shame%20that%20a%20person%20against%20whom%20there%20are%20several%20cases%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs.%20He%20was%20sacked%20from%20our%20party.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20the%20asset%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pramanik%2C%20a%20former%20leader%20of%20the%20Trinamool's%20youth%20wing%2C%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20in%202018%2C%20after%20which%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712238180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F2m4rhch8_mamata-banerjee_625x300_31_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-in-focus-as-pm-modi-mamata-banerjee-court-north-bengal-5374436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cooch%20Behar%2C%20the%20crucial%20north%20Bengal%20district%2C%20became%20subject%20to%20strong%20opposing%20political%20views%20today%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20rallies%20within%2030%20km%20of%20each%20other.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-in-focus-as-pm-modi-mamata-banerjee-court-north-bengal-5374436%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-in-focus-as-pm-modi-mamata-banerjee-court-north-bengal-5374436%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-in-focus-as-pm-modi-mamata-banerjee-court-north-bengal-5374436%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KFC%2C%20Pizza%20Hut%20get%20ready%20to%20bring%20the%20taste%20of%20AI%2C%20here's%20how%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712237490000%2C%22visua