ing%20the%20economy%20the%20third-largest%20in%20the%20world%20from%20fifth%20now%20if%20he%20wins%20a%20third%20term%20in%20a%20row%20as%20polls%20predict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20already%20asked%20officials%20to%20finalise%20plans%20by%20around%20May%20to%20expand%20the%20economy%20to%20%246.69%20trillion%20in%20nominal%20terms%20by%202030%2C%20from%20around%20%243.51%20trillion%20currently%2C%20according%20to%20the%20October%20document.%20Though%20short%20on%20concrete%20details%20of%20how%20to%20achieve%20that%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20basis%20for%20officials'%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20took%20office%20for%20a%20second%20term%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20PM%20Modi%20promised%20to%20take%20the%20economy%20to%20%245%20trillion%20by%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%2C%20but%20partly%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20related%20disruptions%2C%20meeting%20that%20target%20is%20virtually%20impossible%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20six%20years%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20goal%20is%20to%20raise%20per%20capita%20income%20to%20%244%2C418%20from%20around%20%242%2C500%2C%20the%20document%20says%2C%20without%20specifying%20the%20spending%20or%20reforms%20needed%20to%20achieve%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20office%20and%20the%20finance%20ministry%20did%20not%20reply%20to%20requests%20seeking%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20economist%20Saugata%20Bhattacharya%20said%20doubling%20the%20economy%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20difficult%20feat%26quot%3B%20requiring%206%20per%20cent-6.5%20per%20cent%20growth%20for%20the%20next%20seven%20years%20along%20with%20inflation%20of%204.5%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economy%20is%2C%20however%2C%20expected%20to%20have%20grown%20by%20around%208%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%20ended%20March%2031%2C%20the%20fastest%20among%20major%20countries%2C%20on%20the%20back%20of%20strong%20manufacturing%20and%20construction%20activity%20driven%20by%20government%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20senior%20finance%20ministry%20official%2C%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Garg%2C%20said%20growth%20projections%20like%20those%20in%20the%20document%20are%20mostly%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bbackward%20arithmetical%20calculations%26quot%3B%20and%20lack%20any%20%26quot%3Breform%20and%20investment%20plan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsually%20such%20mental%20gymnastics%20based%20on%20arithmetic%20calculations%20and%20assumptions%20are%20meaningless%20unless%20there%20is%20serious%20reform%20and%20investment%20plan%20to%20test%20it%20for%20real%20economy%20dynamics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Garg%2C%20the%20Modi%20government's%20finance%20secretary%20until%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress%20says%20India's%20economic%20growth%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20under%20PM%20Modi%20has%20done%20little%20to%20create%20jobs%20and%20alleviate%20rural%20distress%2C%20while%20the%20disparity%20between%20rich%20and%20poor%20has%20widened.%20The%20document%20says%20PM%20Modi's%20government%20wants%20exports%20of%20goods%20and%20services%20to%20jump%20to%20%241.58%20trillion%20by%202030%20from%20around%20%24700%20billion%2C%20which%20could%20double%20the%20share%20of%20Indian%20exports%20in%20global%20trade%20to%20more%20than%204%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20plans%20to%20focus%20on%2070%20areas%20of%20improvement%20including%20workforce%20skills%20and%20vocational%20training%2C%20critical%20demands%20of%20industry%20leaders%20who%20often%20complain%20about%20the%20skill%20levels%20of%20the%20labour%20force.%20It%20wants%20the%20literacy%20rate%20to%20rise%20to%2082%20per%20cent%20by%202030%20from%20about%2078%20per%20cent%20now%2C%20unemployment%20to%20fall%20to%20less%20than%205%20per%20cent%20from%208%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20labour%20force%20participation%20rate%20to%20jump%20to%20more%20than%2050%20per%20cent%20from%2046%20per%20cent%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20said%20in%20rallies%20he%20needs%20to%20remain%20in%20power%20to%20implement%20measures%20to%20take%20India%20towards%20a%20developed%20economy%20by%202047%2C%20the%20100th%20year%20of%20Independence%2C%20from%20mid-income%20levels%20now.%20He%20has%20not%20spelt%20out%20the%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpinion%20polls%20show%20he%20will%20win%20big%20in%20the%20elections%20starting%20on%20April%2019%20and%20ending%20after%20seven%20phases%20on%20June%201%2C%20with%20vote%20counting%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20led%20by%20PM%20Modi's%20BJP%20could%20win%20nearly%20three-fourths%20of%20parliamentary%20seats%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20could%20hit%20a%20record%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20be%20the%20first%20person%20since%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20to%20win%20three%20consecutive%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712236260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2j2ju7l_narendra-modi_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-sets-ambitious-india-economic-goals-for-probable-3rd-term-5374620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20confident%20of%20winning%20the%20national%20election%20starting%20this%20month%2C%20has%20set%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20roughly%20doubling%20the%20economy%20and%20exports%20this%20decade%2C%20according%20to%20a%20government%20document%20seen%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-sets-ambitious-india-economic-goals-for-probable-3rd-term-5374620%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-sets-ambitious-india-economic-goal