%20heat%20in%20the%20spring%3F%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BPoor%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712231220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fpvg3bv08_man-generic_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fall-the-girls-in-school-like-me-chinese-man-20-diagnosed-with-delusional-love-disorder-5374048%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20story%20of%20a%2020-year-old%20Chinese%20man%20is%20gaining%20attention%20online%20for%20the%20unusual%20disorder%20he%20suffers%20from%20-%20delusional%20love%20disorder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fall-the-girls-in-school-like-me-chinese-man-20-diagnosed-with-delusional-love-disorder-5374048%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fall-the-girls-in-school-like-me-chinese-man-20-diagnosed-with-delusional-love-disorder-5374048%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fall-the-girls-in-school-like-me-chinese-man-20-diagnosed-with-delusional-love-disorder-5374048%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20Andrew%20is%20trying%20to%20stage%20a%20comeback%20amid%20Kate%20Middleton's%20absence%2C%20royal%20commentator%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prince%20Andrew%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660e6ad51caec1275a6cb759%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221467%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrince%20Andrew%20attended%20the%20Thanksgiving%20service%20for%20the%20life%20of%20King%20Constantine%20in%20February.%3Cp%3EANDREW%20MATTHEWS%2FPool%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPrince%20Andrew%20is%20making%20public%20appearances%20with%20the%20royal%20family%20after%20stepping%20down%20in%202