nID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-maybe-trying-lure-ukraine-defenses-from-front-air-force-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia's%20increased%20strikes%20may%20be%20an%20effort%20to%20get%20Ukraine%20to%20move%20air%20defenses%20so%20Russia's%20air%20force%20can%20finally%20play%20a%20bigger%20role%2C%20the%20ISW%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-maybe-trying-lure-ukraine-defenses-from-front-air-force-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Spokesperson%20Exodus%3A%20They%20Were%20Congress's%20Voice%2C%20Now%20They%20Speak%20For%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20once%20the%20Congress's%20defenders%20during%20TV%20debates%20on%20burning%20issues.%20They%20would%20target%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20pose%20tough%20questions.%20They%20now%20articulate%20the%20government's%20position%20and%20slam%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGourav%20Vallabh%20today%20joined%20the%20list%20of%20Congress%20spokespersons%20who%20have%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20A%20familiar%20face%20on%20social%20media%2C%20reels%20of%20Mr%20Vallabh's%20sharp%20jabs%20at%20BJP%20leaders%20would%20often%20go%20viral.%20He%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%20this%20morning%20and%20was%20welcomed%20into%20the%20BJP%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20shortly%20after%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20party's%20lack%20of%20direction.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20neither%20raise%20anti-Sanatan%20slogans%20nor%20abuse%20wealth%20creators%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20resign%20from%20all%20posts%20and%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter%20to%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%3C%