ccessibility%20of%20the%20leadership%20and%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bdynasty%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20parting%20shots.%20Mr%20Shergill%20said%20he%20tried%20to%20meet%20the%20Gandhis%20for%20a%20year%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bpushed%20to%20bow%20down%20before%20people%20because%20they're%20close%20to%20the%20top%20leadership%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Poonawalla%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bforced%20out%20for%20speaking%20against%20(the)%20dynasty%26quot%3B.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20had%20challenged%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20a%20TV%20debate%20on%20their%20vision%20for%20the%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20be%20judged%20on%20merit%2C%20not%20on%20the%20surname%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Joshi%20had%20said%20that%20while%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20heard%20senior%20leaders%20and%20gave%20them%20a%20free%20hand%2C%20that%20did%20not%20happen%20under%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chaturvedi%20quit%20after%20the%20party%20reinstated%20some%20leaders%20she%20had%20accused%20of%20misbehaviour.%20She%20had%20also%20said%20that%20she%20had%20hoped%20that%20the%20party%20would%20give%20her%20a%20chance%20to%20go%20to%20%26quot%3Banother%20level%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20happen%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Jolt%20To%20Narrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vallabh's%20exit%20just%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20the%20Congress%20PR%20campaign.%20Especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20one%20of%20the%20party's%20most%20prominent%20faces%2C%20Supriya%20Shrinate%2C%20is%20under%20fire%20for%20an%20offensive%20social%20media%20post%20against%20BJP%20candidate%20and%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut.%20While%20Ms%20Shrinate%20has%20clarified%20that%20the%20post%20was%20made%20without%20her%20knowledge%2C%20the%20damage%20is%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20senior%20leader%2C%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20was%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20row%20earlier%20this%20year%20over%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%20th