%20the%20shoes%20of%20my%20friend%20late%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C'%20said%20PM%20Modi%20in%20Bihar's%20Jamui%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fnda-to-win-all-40-bihar-seats-pm-modi-campaigns-for-chirag-paswan-124040400674_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fnda-to-win-all-40-bihar-seats-pm-modi-campaigns-for-chirag-paswan-124040400674_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fnda-to-win-all-40-bihar-seats-pm-modi-campaigns-for-chirag-paswan-124040400674_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B%3A%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20Drops%20Broad%20Hint%20Of%20Future%20Plans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExpelled%20Congress%20leader%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%2C%20who%20criticized%20Nehruvian%20secularism%20earlier%20today%2C%20has%20now%20dropped%20a%20broad%20hint%20of%20his%20future%20plans%20with%20a%20resounding%20%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B.%20Asked%20what%20next%2C%20the%2059-year-old%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20plans%2C%20certainly%20I%20am%20joining%20somewhere.%20Will%20declare.%20You%20can%20derive%20meaning%20out%20of%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam%20was%20expelled%20yesterday%20over%20his%20out-of-turn%20comments%20on%20Congress%20ally%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20after%20it%20announced%20candidates%20for%2017%20seats.%20Among%20those%20was%20Mumbai%20North%20West%2C%20a%20seat%20Mr%20Nirupam%20was%20eyeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20leader%20had%20won%20the%20Mumbai%20north%20seat%20in%202009%2C%20but%20lost%20the%20subsequent%20elections%20in%202014%20and%202019%20from%20Mumbai%20North%20and%20Mumbai%20North%20West.%20Today%2C%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20contest%2C%20from%20the%20other%20side%20if%20need%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20North%20West%20seat%20is%20part%20of%20the%20kitty%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%20The%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20has%20fielded%20Amot%20Kirtikar%20from%20the%20seat.%20Mr%20Nirupam%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20become%20an%20MP.%20I%20will%20contest%20and%20defeat%20him%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20MP%2C%20who%20was%20penalized%20by%20the%20Congress%20for%20'indiscipline%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Banti-party%20statements%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20defiant.%C2%A0%20While%20of%20a%20criticism%20spree%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Secularism%20doesn't%20mean%20disregarding%20one's%20own%20religion...%C2%A0%20The%20Nehruvian%20secularism%20which%20has%20no%20place%20for%20religion%20in%20the%20society%2C%20has%20expired%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20other%20barbs%20directed%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Congress%20is%20now%20history%20and%20has%20no%20future%20and%20that%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20is%20a%20merger%20of%20three%20%26quot%3Bsick%20units%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%20There%20are%20five%20power%20centres%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%3A%20The%20three%20Gandhi%20family%20members%2C%20AICC%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20(party%20general%20secretary)%20K%20C%20Venugopal%2C%20Mr%20Nirupam%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20huge%20communication%20gap%20in%20Congress%2C%20there%20are%20many%20lobbies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20being%20heard%20by%20the%20leadership.%20The%20way%20the%20Maharashtra%20alliance%20was%20handled%20was%20wrong.%20Giving%20seats%20to%20Sena%20was%20a%20disastrous%20move%2C%20including%20my%20seat.%20They%20surrendered%20before%20the%20Sena%20and%20gave%20the%20seat%20to%20a%20scamster%20under%20the%20radar%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712228100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fsi0pvelo_sanjay-nirupam-ani_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjai-shri-ram-sanjay-nirupam-drops-broad-hint-of-future-plans-5373650%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Expelled%20Congress%20leader%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%2C%20who%20criticized%20Nehruvian%20secularism%20earlier%20today%2C%20has%20now%20dropped%20a%20broad%20hint%20of%20his%20future%20plans%20with%20a%20resounding%20%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjai-shri-ram-sanjay-nirupam-drops-broad-hint-of-future-plans-5373650%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjai-shri-ram-sanjay-nirupam-drops-broad-hint-of-future-plans-5373650%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjai-shri-ram-sanjay-nirupam-drops-broad-hint-of-future-plans-5373650%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KKR%20Star%20Sunil%20Narine's%20Stunning%20Act%2C%20Shares%20'Fake%20Post'%20Mocking%20RCB%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Narine%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1456-sunil-narine-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Narine%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20truly%20set%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20on%20fire%20with%20his%20breathtaking%20knocks%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20batting-order.%20The%20West%20Indian%20scored%2047%20and%2085%20in%20the%20last%20two%20matches%20for%20his%20franchise%2C%20repaying%20the%20trust%20the%20KKR%20management%20