EThe%20news%20was%20shared%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.massgeneral.org%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2Fworlds-first-genetically-edited-pig-kidney-transplant-into-living-recipient%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20MGH%2C%20which%20is%20Harvard%20Medical%20School's%20largest%20teaching%20hospital%20in%20the%20US%20city%20of%20Boston.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20said%20the%20patient%20Richard%20%26quot%3BRick%26quot%3B%20Slayman%20of%20Weymouth%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20was%20battling%20end-stage%20kidney%20disease%20and%20required%20an%20organ%20transplant.%20On%20March%2016%2C%20his%20doctors%20successfully%20transplanted%20a%20genetically-edited%20pig%20kidney%20into%20his%20body%20over%20a%20four-hour-long%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20said%20that%20Mr%20Slayman's%20kidney%20is%20now%20functioning%20well%20and%20he%20no%20longer%20requires%20dialysis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Slayman%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20that%20being%20able%20to%20leave%20the%20hospital%20and%20go%20home%20was%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20happiest%20moments%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20excited%20to%20resume%20spending%20time%20with%20my%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20loved%20ones%20free%20from%20the%20burden%20of%20dialysis%20that%20has%20affected%20my%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20many%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20underwent%20a%20kidney%20transplant%20from%20a%20dead%20human%20donor.%20However%2C%20last%20year%2C%20the%20transplanted%20kidney%20started%20to%20deteriorate%2C%20prompting%20doctors%20to%20suggest%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20pig%20kidney%20transplant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20it%20not%20only%20as%20a%20way%20to%20help%20me%2C%20but%20a%20way%20to%20provide%20hope%20for%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20who%20need%20a%20transplant%20to%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20pig%20kidney%20he%20received%20was%20modified%20by%20Cambridge-based%20pharmaceutical%20company%20eGenesis%20to%20remove%20%26quot%3Bharmful%20pig%20genes%20and%20add%20certain%20human%20genes%20to%20improve%20its%20compatibility%20with%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20noted%20that%20for%20this%20procedure%2C%20it%20leveraged%20its%20legacy%20as%20the%20pioneer%20of%20the%20world's%20first%20successful%20human%20organ%20transplant%20-%20a%20kidney%20-%20in%201954.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20referenced%20ongoing%20research%20conducted%20in%20collaboration%20with%20eGenesis%20on%20xenotransplantation%20(the%20transplantation%20of%20organs%20between%20different%20species)%20over%20the%20preceding%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20approved%20the%20procedure%20under%20a%20single%20Expanded%20Access%20Protocol%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20compassionate%20use%2C%20typically%20reserved%20for%20patients%20with%20life-threatening%20conditions%20to%20grant%20them%20access%20to%20experimental%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transplant%20team%20celebrated%20this%20milestone%20as%20a%20historic%20advancement%20that%20could%20offer%20a%20promising%20solution%20to%20the%20global%20organ%20shortage%2C%20particularly%20benefiting%20ethnic%20minority%20communities%20who%20are%20disproportionately%20affected%20by%20the%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20abundant%20supply%20of%20organs%20resulting%20from%20this%20technological%20advance%20may%20go%20far%20to%20finally%20achieve%20health%20equity%20and%20offer%20the%20best%20solution%20to%20kidney%20failure%20-%20a%20well-functioning%20kidney%20-%20to%20all%20patients%20in%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Winfred%20Williams%2C%20Mr%20Slayman's%20doctor%20at%20MGH.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712227500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fv5abun3g_pig-kidney-transplant-patient_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22origi