%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon-backed%20humanoid%20firm%20Agility%20Robotics%20laid%20off%20a%20'small%20number'%20of%20staff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222629%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Digit%20Amazon%20robot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653174e396908fd7cdb2e027%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221845%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAgility%20Robotics'%20bipedal%20robot%20Digit.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAgility%20Robotics%20said%20it%20laid%20off%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bsmall%20number%26quot%3B%20of%20employees%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%2C%20which%20has%20invested%20in%20the%20company%2C%20is%20testing%20its%20robot%20in%20a%20research%20facility.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAgility%20plans%20to%20open%20a%20new%20factory%20in%20Oregon%20later%20this%20year%20to%20mass-produce%20its%20Digit%20robot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAgility%20Robotics%20reduced%20the%20size%20of%20its%20workforce%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20job%20cuts%20affected%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20number%26quot%3B%20of%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20Agility's%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20structure%20the%20company%20for%20success%2C%20we%20have%20parted%20ways%20with%20a%20small%20number%20of%20employees%20that%20were%20not%20central%20to%20core%20product%20development%20and%20commercialization%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20is%20testing%20its%20Agility's%20Digit%20robots%20in%20a%20research%20and%20development%20facility%20near%20Seattle.%20The%20tech%20giant%20has%20previously%20funded%20Agility%20as%20part%20of%20its%20first%20round%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aboutamazon.com%2Fnews%2Finnovation-at-amazon%2Fintroducing-the-1-billion-amazon-industrial-innovation-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestments%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20its