-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20uses%20innovative%20methods%20of%20farming%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20at%20the%20KVK%20suggested%20some%20biofertilisers%20to%20salvage%20the%20turmeric%20crop%2C%20and%20it%20worked.%20They%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20preserve%20the%20soil%20and%20prevent%20further%20damage%20was%20by%20moving%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%2058-year-old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%202008%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20save%20his%20land%2C%20soil%20and%20crops%2C%20he%20slowly%20stopped%20using%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides.%20He%20also%20started%20practising%20crop%20rotation%20to%20ensure%20soil%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20I%20plant%20pulses%2C%20I%20ensure%20that%20I%20change%20the%20crop%20for%20the%20next%20year.%20I%20also%20planted%20nerium%20as%20a%20border%20crop%20to%20absorb%20pollutants%20and%20grow%20%3Cem%3Eagathi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%26amp%3B%20maize%20around%20the%20field%20as%20a%20barrier%20crop%20to%20prevent%20the%20entry%20of%20pests%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20constructed%20a%20vermicompost%20production%20unit%20in%202008%20which%20produces%20over%206%20tonnes%20per%20year.%20He%20uses%20this%20vermicompost%2C%20neem%20cakes%20and%20castor%20cakes%20as%20fertilisers.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20biogas%20plant%20that%20converts%20the%20waste%20into%20energy%20and%20purifies%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%2C%20he%20utilises%20%3Cem%3Epanchakavya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20solution%20made%20of%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%2C%20curd%2C%20ghee%2C%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20used%20as%20a%20fertiliser)%20spray%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20homemade%20spray%20containing%20ginger%2C%20garlic%20%26amp%3B%20chillies%20for%20controlling%20pests%20and%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20everything%20was%20going%20well%2C%20Saravanan%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20grow%20fodder%20for%2