3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20original%20name%2C%20people%20of%20all%20faiths%20were%20welcomed%20at%20the%20hotel%20by%20Panda%20who%20was%20affectionately%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Thakurmoshai%E2%80%99.%20According%20to%20an%20article%20in%20the%20digital%20repository%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%2C%20there%20was%20one%20time%20when%20a%20group%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20found%20themselves%20inside%20the%20hotel.%20In%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20meeting%20where%20they%20were%20discussing%20their%20retaliation%20against%20the%20British%2C%20there%20was%20an%20unexpected%20police%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20tells%20of%20Mangobindo%E2%80%99s%20bravado%20as%20he%20positioned%20himself%20at%20the%20doorway%2C%20refusing%20to%20yield.%20He%20remained%20steadfast%20until%20the%20police%20finally%20retreated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%20this%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20highlighted%20how%20a%20secret%20room%20was%20built%20inside%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F95258%2Findia-food-culture-britain-history-bengali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20back%20exit%20that%20led%20to%20a%20secret%20passageway%20outside.%20The%20arrangement%20was%20apt%20for%20the%20revolutionaries%20who%20would%20often%20discuss%20their%20plans%20at%20the%20hotel%20and%20want%20to%20escape%20when%20a%20police%20van%20approached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20was%20always%20supportive%20of%20the%20freedom%20fighters%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20current%20owner%20Arunanghshu%20Panda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCozw7phJbjw%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2