th%20local%20tailors%20to%20make%20the%20bags%20and%20meet%20the%20steadily%20growing%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20quit%20their%20respective%20jobs%20and%20throw%20themselves%20into%20growing%20their%20venture.%20The%20name%20comes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276764%2Fmadurai-couple-quits-jobs-eco-friendly-cloth-manjapai-yellow-bag-plastic-alternative%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20Manjappai%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20means%20a%20yellow-coloured%20cloth%20bag)%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Tamil%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20revive%20this%20tradition%2C%20the%20company%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20bags%20made%20of%20cotton%20and%20jute%20that%20serve%20different%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20offer%20products%20like%20packaging%20bags%2C%20garment%20protector%20bags%2C%20totes%2C%20and%20drawstring%20bags.%20%E2%80%9COur%20products%20start%20from%20Rs%2020%20and%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%20200.%20They%20are%20mostly%20made%20based%20on%20the%20client%E2%80%99s%20requirements.%20We%20mainly%20market%20our%20products%20through%20our%20website%20or%20through%20several%20social%20media%20platforms.%20We%20also%20sell%20our%20products%20at%20our%20own%20office%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20stitches%202%2C000%20to%203%2C000%20bags%20a%20day!%20And%20the%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake%20was%20that%20they%20earned%20Rs%203%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20find%20their%20journey%20inspiring%3F%20Here%20is%20a%20short%20video%20about%20their%20sustainable%20bags%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%2248