0a%20catastrophe.%20But%20as%20they%20would%20soon%20discover%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20spent%20the%20majority%20of%20three%20years%20having%20countless%20meetings%20with%20government%20officials%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20ministers%20where%20he%20convinced%20the%20room%20that%20Jawai%20was%20the%20natural%20habitat%20of%20leopards%2C%20and%20that%20the%20area%20housed%20tremendous%20tourism%20potential.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20Government%20gave%20a%20premature%20termination%20notice%20to%20all%20the%20mines.%20The%20activity%20was%20soon%20discontinued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20who%20had%20quit%20a%20lucrative%20job%20in%20winemaking%20to%20turn%20his%20attention%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20now%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179096%2Fifs-officer-hero-mumbai-leopard-human-conflict-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20envisioned%20that%20the%20land%20that%20he%20had%20fought%20so%20hard%20to%20protect%20would%20now%20be%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20the%20leopards%20and%20those%20who%20loved%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge%20stands%20on%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20is%20a%20gold%20standard%20in%20how%20luxury%20does%20not%20need%20to%20be%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20success%20story%20in%20conservation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20who%20is%20now%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20a%20successful%20boutique%20lodge%2C%20recalls%20his%20early%20days%20of%20renting%20out%20a%20room%20in%20his%20driver%E2%80%99s%20home.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20I%20was%20fighting%20against%20the%20mining%20in%20the%20area.%20I%20had%20to%20stay%20on-site%2C%20so%20I%20lived%20with%20my%20driver%20who%20was%20a%20local%20in%20Bera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20used%20to%20make%20fun%20of%20me%20saying%20that%20I%20was%20living%20with%20my%20driver.%20But%20someone%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20mining%20project%20and%20I%20was%20very%20passionate%20about%20it.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F36889%2Finternational-day-of-snow-leopard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20very%20clear.%20I%20thought%2C%20if%20nobody%20does%20it%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20observation%20on%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20part%20has%20been%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20locals%20towards%20the%20leopards.%20Once%20frightened%20about%20leopard%20attacks%2C%20he%20says%20the%20locals%20(aside%20from%20the%20Rabari%20community)%20would%20poison%20the%20beasts.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20today%2C%20due%20to%20the%20tourism%20model%20in%20Bera%2C%20every%20villager%20is%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20associated%20with%20it.%20Since%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20tourism%20here%20is%20safaris%20to%20see%20the%20leopard%2C%20they%20understand%20how%20important%20the%20animal%20is%20for%20their%20welfare.%20Today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F12694%2Fvanamitra-suresh-conserve-wildlife-india-leopards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehumans%20and%20leopards%20coexist%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge%20has%20seven%20eco%20friendly%20cottages%20where%20people%20can%20stay%20along%20with%20safaris%20where%20guests%20can%20enjoy%20spotting%20the%20leopards%20and%20hyenas%20in%20the%20wild%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22