0at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20used%20to%20come%20really%20close.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFear%20was%20the%20last%20thing%20on%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20He%20understood%20the%20wild%20and%20it%20understood%20him%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20these%20learnings%20that%20he%20shares%20with%20his%20guests%20on%20the%20safari%20rides%20at%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge.%20He%20urges%20people%20to%20revel%20in%20the%20beauty%20of%20watching%20leopards%20and%20humans%20live%20together%20here%20but%20cautions%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20national%20park.%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20see%20how%20wonderful%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20in%20over%20decades%20there%20has%20been%20zero%20human-animal%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20years%20when%20Singh%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20documenting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fmeet-the-ladakhis-who-helped-save-indias-snow-leopards-with-innovative-ideas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20wild%20cats%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20building%20his%20dream%20homestay%20that%20started%20with%20three%20rooms%20and%20has%20now%20grown%20to%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stone%20construction%20is%20a%20paradise%20and%20is%20managed%20by%20staff%20from%20the%20region.%20The%20produce%20too%20is%20sourced%20from%20the%20village%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20Singh%20notes%20how%20they%20are%20part%20of%20the%20economy%20supporting%20local%20people.%20%E2%80%9COur%20main%20motto%20is%3A%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20sell%20rooms%2C%20we%20sell%20experiences%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20emphasises%20going%20on%20to%20add%20that%20their%20no%20TV%20policy%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20this.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20guests%20to%20be%20outside%20the%20room%20and%20enjoy%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%2